    "By leveraging the power of SonarQube and the expertise of CISQ, software products can be not only functional and reliable but also environmentally friendly and efficient: in fact, with the Automated Source Code CISQ Performance Efficiency Measure (ASCPEM) specification, we can establish a standard measure of performance efficiency by detecting violations of good architectural and coding practices that may result in inefficient operation, such as performance degradation or excessive use of processor resources.The second challenge was to implement a reliable and accurate monitoring tool to calculate and track carbon emissions to calculate emissions at different granularity levels, identify anomalies, and prioritize areas for improvement.",
